TEUM the reason most of you complainers about non movement of Teum is why most of you will never create wealth investing Jessie Livermore quote posted beforeIt never was my thinking that made the big money for me It always was my sitting Got that My sitting tight It is no trick at all to be right on the market You always find lots of early bulls in bull markets and early bears in bear markets Ive known many men who were right at exactly the right time and began buying and selling stocks when prices were at the very level which should show the greatest profit And their experience invariably matched mine that is they made no real money out of it Men who can both be right and sit tight are uncommon I found it one of the hardest things to learn But it is only after a stock operator has firmly grasped this that he can make big money It is literally true that millions come easier to a trader after he knows how to trade than hundreds did in the days of his ignorance
